# ZFS file system

## Redirect

ZFS is not supported on WacOS due to ZFS being proprietary. However, OpenZFS is supported and is open source. [Read about WacOS support for OpenZFS here](https://github.com/seanpm2001/WacOS/wiki/OpenZFS/)
